163
00:13:14,699 --> 00:13:15,990
Rym: It can't just be the attendance.

164
00:13:16,210 --> 00:13:23,426
Rym: You also have the production pipeline, the system and bureaucracy that causes the event to actually occur.

165
00:13:24,930 --> 00:13:29,103
Rym: Because some events have attendance and not logistics, and that is how you get a DashCon.

166
00:13:30,493 --> 00:13:35,730
