167
00:13:36,412 --> 00:13:40,310
Scott: You can do a thing by hand and handcraft a thing, but then that's it.

168
00:13:40,410 --> 00:13:41,008
Scott: You did it once.

169
00:13:42,271 --> 00:13:45,389
Scott: Alternatively, you can create a machine that makes the thing.

170
00:13:45,730 --> 00:13:50,349
Scott: If you build a machine that runs a convention, that convention is just going to keep happening.

171
00:13:51,233 --> 00:13:55,669
Scott: If you, on your own, make a convention happen with your will, you might do it.

172
00:13:56,070 --> 00:13:58,650
