178
00:14:28,951 --> 00:14:32,310
Scott: It'll just keep getting contracts to make more movies.

179
00:14:32,350 --> 00:14:38,589
Rym: It's that very powerful idea that the most valuable thing you can make is the machine that makes the machine, not the machine itself.

180
00:14:39,230 --> 00:14:43,890
