469
00:34:38,452 --> 00:34:58,652
Scott: So, for example, you can put one of your portals way high up in the level and put another one in a tiny room where you're hiding and now you can snipe at the whole level from a tiny room and if someone wants to shoot you, they can come find you or they can just shoot in this portal that's prominently above the whole level and that they can see bullets coming out of and killing their friend.

