618
00:45:20,721 --> 00:45:24,096
Scott: There's some sort of like automatic, just there's no health packs or anything.

619
00:45:24,116 --> 00:45:26,315
Scott: There's no healing, medkits, bandages.

620
00:45:26,618 --> 00:45:36,840
