622
00:45:58,001 --> 00:46:04,859
Rym: Old school FPSs would have the health as a, this is a finite resource you have to manage, the more damage you take, the more likely it is to die.

623
00:46:05,561 --> 00:46:10,898
Rym: This, the way Splitgate does this specifically, gives you this very specific feeling.

624
00:46:10,918 --> 00:46:20,759
